.SH NAME
SVGAElement.port \- SVGAElement: port property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]port\f[B]\f[R] property of the \f[CR]SVGAElement\f[R]
interface returns a string representing the port component, if any, of
the referenced URL.
.PP
This property can be set, to change the URL\(cqs port.
.SH VALUE
A string.
